<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement | CourtScope"><section class="hero"><div class="prose-width"><p class="eyebrow">Public policy</p><h1>Accessibility Statement</h1><p class="lede">CourtScope targets WCAG 2.2 AA.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="prose-width"><div class="card"><p>We support keyboard navigation, visible focus, non-color-only meaning, accessible forms, text alternatives for charts, and responsive layouts. Report an accessibility barrier through the contact page.</p><h2>What controls</h2><p>Official source terms, applicable law, dataset-specific notices, and the current published CourtScope methodology control where they are more specific. Contact <a href="mailto:info@courtscope.org">info@courtscope.org</a> for questions.</p><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 11, 2026</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>